These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: canadian, pakistani, spanish, japanese
1. Nationality:pakistani is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:japanese is between Nationality:canadian and Nationality:pakistani##2
3. Nationality:japanese is on the right of Nationality:canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | canadian | japanese | pakistani | spanish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: grapefruit, kale, spinach, apple
1. Food:grapefruit is on the left of Food:apple##1
2. Food:kale is in an odd position##4
3. Food:kale is on the left or right of Food:grapefruit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | kale | grapefruit | apple | spinach |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: fantasy, scientific, superhero, satire
1. Movie-Genre:satire is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:fantasy##3
2. Movie-Genre:fantasy is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:superhero is between Movie-Genre:satire and Movie-Genre:scientific##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | satire | superhero | scientific |

 #################################
 
