.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: papaya, pear, radish, asparagus
1. Food:pear == Food:pear##1
2. Food:asparagus is on the left or right of Food:radish##3
3. Food:radish is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:papaya is in an even position##4
5. Food:asparagus is on the left of Food:pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | radish | asparagus | pear | papaya |

